  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contact - ParenWorks Systems</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Get in touch with ParenWorks Systems for your Common Lisp development needs" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../static/parenworks.css" @href="/static/parenworks/parenworks.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&amp;family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="nav-container">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
          <span class="paren">(</span>ParenWorks<span class="paren">)</span>
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="active">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    
    <main>
      <section class="page-header">
        <h1>Contact Me</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Let's discuss your next project</p>
      </section>

      <section class="contact-content">
        <div class="contact-grid">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>
              Whether you have a specific project in mind or just want to explore how 
              Common Lisp can benefit your organisation, I'd love to hear from you.
            </p>
            
            <div class="contact-methods">
              <div class="contact-method">
                <span class="contact-icon">üìß</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>Email</h3>
                  <p><a href="mailto:hello@parenworks.systems">hello@parenworks.systems</a></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="contact-method">
                <span class="contact-icon">üí¨</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>IRC</h3>
                  <p>#parenworks on Libera.Chat</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="contact-method">
                <span class="contact-icon">üêô</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>GitHub</h3>
                  <p><a href="https://github.com/parenworks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/parenworks</a></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="response-time">
              <pre class="code-block small"><code><span class="keyword">(defvar</span> <span class="symbol">*response-time*</span>
  <span class="string">"Usually within 24 hours"</span><span class="keyword">)</span></code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-form-container">
            <h2>Send a Message</h2>
            <div id="form-status" class="form-status" style="display: none;"></div>
            <form class="contact-form" id="contact-form" method="post" action="#">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required="required" placeholder="Your name" />
              </div>
              
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required="required" placeholder="your@email.com" />
              </div>
              
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required="required" placeholder="Tell me about your project or question..."></textarea>
              </div>
              
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full" id="submit-btn">
                <span class="code-inline">(send-message)</span>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="faq-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Why should I choose Common Lisp for my project?</h3>
            <p>Common Lisp offers unmatched flexibility, powerful abstractions, and a proven track record in complex systems. It's particularly well-suited for AI, DSLs, and systems requiring long-term maintainability.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can you integrate with our existing systems?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. Common Lisp has excellent FFI capabilities and I have extensive experience integrating with C, Python, Java, and various databases and APIs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What's your typical project timeline?</h3>
            <p>It varies by scope, but my REPL-driven development approach typically delivers working prototypes faster than traditional methods. I'll provide detailed estimates after our initial consultation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you offer ongoing support?</h3>
            <p>Yes, I offer maintenance and support packages for all my projects. I believe in building long-term relationships with my clients.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <span class="paren">(</span>ParenWorks<span class="paren">)</span>
